 25.0d-12 [s] "FrL" is duration of each frame in file "Frames.dat".
  2.5d-12 [s] "tstep" is the computation time step "dt". FrL/tstep must be integer >= 10. 
               If you try "tstep" > FrL/10, code changes "tstep" to FrL/10.   
  0.d-12  [s]  Start Time of computations must be 20 (or more) "tstep" prior to cental time of 1st frame.
 65.d-12  [s]  End-of-computation time. It must be > [central time of last orded frame +FrL/2 + tstep]       
 50.d-12  [s] "tiInf" is the time chosen for printing "...LineInfo.dat", "...EmiAbso.dat", "EffSpIns.dat",  "AlongCeLOS.dat", "Image...dat", "SpInDi...dat"  
  0.01        "W2max" is maximal allowed probability of crossing two BSs by one LOS  
